Version 3 plus: reflection and filtering out photons hitting the outer disk

compilation: 
gcc mtc_carlo_uni.c quadrat.c -lm -DDEBUG -o mtc_uni

Important parameters:
temp : electron temperature, c.a. 100 keV
taumax: radial optical thickness  0.5-2 
number_of_MC_steps - 
cold_refl 0 - no refl, 1 - with refl.
rad_temp - max. temperature of the soft photons

output: mcomp_number.dat, column 1- energy, 2 - spectrum (F_E)
